         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">30/7/94 ¶ Near Midnight ¶  ¶ Was sorry to miss your visit, dear Mr Shillinglaw, which would have been a spright one! That a man of genius should carry for some miles an umbrella back I regard almost a...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">94.07.30</p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To John Shillinglaw</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">Box 246/2, Shillinglaw papers, La Trobe Australian manuscripts collection, State Library of Victoria, Melbourne.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">30/7/94</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">Near Midnight</hi>
               </seg>
            </p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Was sorry to miss your visit, dear Mr Shillinglaw, which would have been a spright one! That a man of genius should carry for some miles an umbrella back I regard almost an unheard of affair. I was out on a<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">double</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>errand of<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
               <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="">
                  <hi rend="underline">charity</hi>
               </seg>
               <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>even on the evening of the mail for the whole eastern hemisphere!</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>But to return to the umbrella! As I am often lost in thought, I am apt to leave such trivialities of the outer world behind; but the "moral" has been for years to me thus far to purchase the cheapest umbrella in the market only, as when one has gone astray, not all are so attentive as you.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Salve!</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Among my posthumous memoires this may serve as a treatise on umbrellas.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
   </text>
